{"tid":1442802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"夏日炎炎環保BBQ神器","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:50:02.000Z","uid":263141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4d665ab9a227dfa1ec62a1d0a3f814a9d3c243","tid":1442802,"uid":263141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇見過一種爐係&lsquo;聚焦太陽能&rsquo;黎煮食物嫁呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/DNC4DTg5qyWYHcu58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FDNC4DTg5qyWYHcu58&h=1629b751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日小弟就係想黎介紹尼款爐同原理<br />\n原理係聚焦陽光既熱能去&lsquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">焗</span></span>&rsquo;熟食物<br />\n唔洗用電，方便又環保<br />\n<br />\n如果大家冇咁多budget既話可以試下用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">化妝鏡/放大鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n**請勿用於長時間照射於人/動物**<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2844f1400ea44ec58e9f5b0cc1b3e7a9a50e8531","tid":1442802,"uid":263141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2404dd3763e4cb817904090d0deafaa1f169ad2a","tid":1442802,"uid":263141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07f80b12f4fbd5d578c22b4c80b1015fbc7ececa","tid":1442802,"uid":263141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔知做乜upload唔到相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係尼款爐既link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gq.com.tw/mobile/blog/iscar/detail-3139.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com.tw%2Fmobile%2Fblog%2Fiscar%2Fdetail-3139.html%3F&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=2f5c6b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gq.com.tw/mobile/blog/iscar/detail-3139.html?</a>"},{"pid